data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! SEEING IS BELIEVING! AWESOME FLOOR PLAN WITH SOARING CEILINGS! CONCRETE BLOCK CONSTRUCTION WITH VERY LOW MASTER HOA FEE!  "Nestled in the charming Calusa Creek community, this very nice 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. As you step through the front door, you are welcomed by an abundance of natural light that accentuates the open floor plan, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The spacious living room is ideal for family gatherings or entertaining friends, featuring elegant finishes and a seamless flow into the modern kitchen. Imagine preparing delicious meals in the well-appointed kitchen with high-end appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient breakfast bar. The master suite provides a tranquil retreat, boasting a private ensuite bathroom and generous closet space. The two additional bedrooms are perfect for guests, children, there's even a home office / media room! Step outside to the backyard oasis, where a covered patio invites you to relax and unwind, creating a peaceful escape. With the Sunseeker Resort distance away, you'll have easy access to world-class amenities, dining, and entertainment options. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Calusa Creek gem your own and experience the best of Punta Gorda living LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION !it's Just off the I-75 INTERSTATE AND HWY 17 Call today to schedule your showing appointment
